The '''Dangerous Species Act''' was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] legislature which decreed that any [[Species/Legends|species]] that was dangerous and interfered with Imperial occupation of a [[Planet/Legends|planet]] was subject to eradication by the Empire. The act was only intended to apply to non-[[Sentience/Legends|sentient]] lifeforms or wild beasts.

